Claude Puntel-Sessions

Wichita rich cross culture, going from Wichi…WHAT? To Wichi…WOW!

Jan 29, 2016

Mom, wife, entrepreneur, professional cultural trainer, language instructor, translator. Transplanted to Wichita from the beautiful south of France. Loves languages, accents, and has a passion to help people bridge the gap between cultures and embrace differences and riches.

Favorite Thing About Wichita:
“Love the unlimited opportunities to meet extraordinary people in the big small town.”
